
# Beware: using this fake response to a REPORT LUNS command takes no
# account of the SELECT REPORT field in the cdb. See the definition
# of that command and field in spc7r05.pdf or later.
# Also decoding the LUNs may depend of the knowledge of the LU_CONG
# bit in the standard INQUIRY response.
#
# the author thinks this LUN data might match:
#    sg_luns --select=0x10 --lu_cong --decode --inhex=luns_lu_cong.hex

# report_luns_parameter_data
00 00 00 10 00 00 00 00

00 01 00 00 00 00 00 00
00 01 00 02 00 00 00 00

